# TypeScript Configuration Rules

## Base Configuration
```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "strict": true,
    "target": "ES2022",
    "lib": ["dom", "dom.iterable", "esnext"],
    "jsx": "react-jsx",
    "module": "esnext",
    "moduleResolution": "node",
    "noEmit": true,
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["./src/*"]
    }
  }
}
```

